Leypa File API Library for Nim Contracts
issue.body:
child to #1

1. A WASM Contract in Nim should be able to import & use a `leypa-file` library in the form  of a nimble package.
2. The package must offer following operations:
 - [ ] CREATE
 - [ ] READ
 - [ ] UPDATE
